Go to the selected directory (for example "genesis")

./build.sh

sudo ../pack.sh 256
qemu -hda hd.img -serial mon:stdio


../qemu hd.img  

b *0x7c00
b *0x7c70

Open another terminal and run ddd &

NOTE:
Edit the File browser preferences 
  - on TAB  Media deselect Browse media when inserted

be sure that a copy of files .gdbinit and  build.sh is in the directory 
(or a symbolic link to the file located in MK)

